ogX.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>  <p><strong>Output for:</strong></p>  <pre><code>$avatar = get_avatar( $comment-&gt;comment_author_email, $size = '48', $default = bloginfo( 'template_directory' ).'/img/admin.jpg' );  if( $avatar !== false ) {     echo $avatar;  } </code></pre>  <p><strong>is:</strong> <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/G9MsT.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/G9MsT.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>